\[PQ + F_1 Q = PQ + F_2 Q - F_2 Q + F_1 Q = 14 - F_2 Q + F_1 Q.\]We want to maximize $14 - F_2 Q + F_1 Q,$ which is the same as minimizing $F_2 Q - F_1 Q.$

